      <title>欧盟考虑退出俄罗斯液化天然气，欧洲天然气价格波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/european-gas-prices-swing-as-eu-considers-exiting-russian-lng</link>
